The paper deals with object recognition, which is a core topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of convolutional neural networks (CNNs) and other computational models also suggests that it could belong to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE) sub-categories.
